  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460010/extras/45af91609102bd6b979f6cd844fc3d03.avif?t=1687515116\" width=648 height=246 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460010/extras/aded4df2df5f351b565a54586bdc320b.avif?t=1687515116\" width=367 height=79 /></span>.<br><br>Epic Pandemonium is a classic run-and-gun action game with a strong focus on boss battles. Inspired by the 16-bit Contra saga.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460010/extras/bfdf2580a08ed7c861af7c949436c99b.avif?t=1687515116\" width=367 height=79 /></span>.<br><br><br>In the year 2xxx, scientists from the University of Texas make an astonishing<br>discovery: a portal to another universe. However, something goes wrong, and<br>thousands of creatures emerge from it, known as the Demonium.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460010/extras/dec8ba7aa1b52f51a1142d70f5a5d8f9.avif?t=1687515116\" width=367 height=79 /></span>.<br><br><br>- 6 levels of pure action.<br>- 18 Bosses<br>- Variety of enemies<br>- Game entirely in pixel art 16-bit style.<br>- 5 different weapons<br>- Pandemonium difficulty level<br> <strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100 % steam deck compatible use Proton Experimental</h2></strong>",
